  rw [h3]
  simp [ENNReal.mul_pos, c_pos, hp1_pos, hp2_pos]
```

Now we need to show `eLpNorm ... ‚Č§ ‚ąě`. This is true since `eLpNorm ...` is finite.
`eLpNorm f r őĹ` is defined as `‚ąę‚ĀĽ (t : ‚ĄĚ‚Č•0), (f.toENNReal * (őľ s ^ r‚ĀĽ¬Ļ).toENNReal) dőĹ s`.
This is a real number. So it's less than `‚ąě`.

```tactics
