We need to prove that if `T` has restricted weak type `(p, p')` with constant `c > 0`, then for any measurable sets `F` and `G`, the inequality `eLpNorm (T (F.indicator (fun _ ‚Ü¶ 1))) 1 (őĹ.restrict G) ‚Č§ c * (őľ F) ^ p‚ĀĽ¬Ļ.toReal * (őĹ G) ^ p'‚ĀĽ¬Ļ.toReal` holds. 

